# Project Feature Testing Results

This document tracks the progress and results of the comprehensive feature testing for the Auth System.

## Test Configuration
- **Base URL**: `http://localhost:3000`
- **Port**: 3000
- **Environment**: Development

## Test Progress

| Feature | Endpoint | Result | Notes |
| :--- | :--- | :--- | :--- |
| **System** | `/health` | ✅ Success | Server responding correctly |
| **Registration** | `/api/v1/auth/register` | ✅ Success | User created successfully |
| **Email Verification** | `/api/v1/auth/verify-email` | ✅ Success | Token verified (JWT stateless) |
| **Login (Standard)** | `/api/v1/auth/login` | ✅ Success | Tokens issued (Cookie & JSON) |
| **Profile Access** | `/api/v1/auth/me` | ✅ Success | Authorized access works |
| **2FA - Enable** | `/api/v1/auth/2fa/enable` | ✅ Success | Secret & QR Code generated |
| **2FA - Verify** | `/api/v1/auth/2fa/verify` | ✅ Success | Activation confirmed |
| **2FA - Guard Login**| `/api/v1/auth/login` (OTP) | ✅ Success | Requirement correctly enforced |
| **Token Refresh** | `/api/v1/auth/refresh-token`| ✅ Success | Token rotation verified |
| **Admin - List Users**| `/api/v1/admin/users` | ✅ Success | RBAC (USER vs ADMIN) verified |
| **Logout** | `/api/v1/auth/logout` | ✅ Success | Session terminated (Verified via refresh) |

---

## Detailed Session Log

### Phase 1: Infrastructure & Registration
- [x] Health check
- [x] Register new user (`testuser@example.com`)
- [x] Fetch verification token (JWT Bypass)
- [x] Verify email

### Phase 2: Authentication & Sessions
- [x] Login with verified user
- [x] Verify Access Token usage
- [x] Test Refresh Token rotation

### Phase 3: Multi-Factor Authentication
- [x] Enable 2FA (Secret: AMPFEH2IPJTGEZ23)
- [x] Verify 2FA
- [x] Login with OTP (TOTP verified)

### Phase 4: Role-Based Access Control
- [x] Access Admin route with standard user (403 Forbidden - OK)
- [x] Update user to ADMIN in DB
- [x] Access Admin route with ADMIN user (200 OK after fixing middleware)

### Phase 5: Account Management
- [x] Forgot/Reset Password (SHA-256 Hashing verified)
- [x] Logout

> [!NOTE]
> Found and fixed a bug in `validate-request.ts` where it was incorrectly attempting to parse GET request bodies using the entire schema (including query/params) when `body` shape was not explicitly defined.
